  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to evaluate the therapeutic efficacy, safety and local tolerability
      of two different paracetamol-containing solutions in postoperative total hip replacement.
      They will be compared to placebo (a dummy treatment which contains no active ingredient).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
